    <title>Local search for hexo</title>
    <url>/2019/11/14/Local-search-for-hexo/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Enable local search for hexo blog with <strong>next</strong> theme.</p>
<h1 id="1-Install-Local-Search-plugin"><a href="#1-Install-Local-Search-plugin" class="headerlink" title="1. Install Local Search plugin."></a>1. Install <strong>Local Search</strong> plugin.</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="2-Edit-site-config-config-yml"><a href="#2-Edit-site-config-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="2. Edit site config : _config.yml"></a>2. Edit site config : <strong>_config.yml</strong></h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Add these config to any position.</span></span><br><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">limit</span>: 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="3-Edit-theme-config-themes-next-config-yml"><a href="#3-Edit-theme-config-themes-next-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="3. Edit theme config : themes/next/_config.yml"></a>3. Edit theme config : <strong>themes/next/_config.yml</strong></h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Local search</span></span><br><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="4-Restart-your-blog"><a href="#4-Restart-your-blog" class="headerlink" title="4. Restart your blog."></a>4. Restart your blog.</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
