    <title>01-Deploy hexo blog to githubPage</title>
    <url>/2019/10/31/Deploy-hexo-blog-to-githubPage/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<ol>
<li><p>Install hexo-deployer-git.</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> hexo_project</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
